  <prompt>Implement Service Bus subscription consumer that processes MembershipChangedEvent and upserts/deletes `sprk_userentityassociation` rows. Idempotent: keyed on {personId, entityRecordId, sourceField} — duplicate delivery safe.</prompt>
  <goal>Handler consumes from `recon-junction-updater` subscription. Add → upsert. Remove → delete. Update → upsert (overwrite role/timestamp). Idempotent on duplicate delivery.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-001">In-process BackgroundService</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec FR-2P2.4">Idempotency keyed on {personId, entityRecordId, sourceField}</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
