  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + FR-2P2.4</step>
    <step order="1">Implement MembershipJunctionUpdater (event-handler logic)</step>
    <step order="2">Implement MembershipJunctionUpdaterHost : BackgroundService (subscription consumer loop)</step>
    <step order="3">Upsert by composite key (idempotency)</step>
    <step order="4">Unit tests: add/remove/update; duplicate delivery; cancellation</step>
    <step order="5">Integration test: event published → row appears in junction table</step>
